➜成毅袁冰妍见面会全程零互动，剧粉被打脸暴走，何至于形同陌路？
http://www.sohu.com/a/419871023_162238	37129
<p class="ql-align-justify">昨天晚上，琉璃云歌会如约上线</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">作为剧粉，云歌会算是本橘近期最期待的一个活动了</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">本以为它会像之前的见面会一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">甜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200921/ae6315fcd3524a978ffb2bbbff035857.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">甜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200921/d0925029e8fc417791e0934e0f11e0c5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">甜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200921/717aeba31cee41e18c6cab547c4f57bf.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
