<p class="ql-align-justify">比如音乐领域，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">唱了几首影视剧插曲；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200921/b4128896ef704ce7be9863897b88475b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
